   The description of the problem:
   I have a project needs to parse excel in the number of amount.
   For example,the amount is 1835.6, But I got such a result 1835.600000000001  when i used poi parsing it  with the os linux  64-bit  .
   This is the code:
   import org.apache.poi.hssf.usermodel.HSSFCell;
   public double getNumberCellValueByPoi(HSSFSheet hssfsheet, int i, int j)
    {
      HSSFCell hssfcell = getCell(hssfsheet, i, j);
      double value=hssfcell.getNumericCellValue();
      return value;
   }

   The result   output in  the console is 1835.600000000001。But if  i run the project with the  windows or linux  32-bit ,the result is right.

     I need your reply quickly .Thank you very much.
